Preservation solutions for static cold storage in DCD and DBD liver transplantation in the United States.
There were no differences between groups among DCD LTs in the earlier eras, and among DBD LTs in al eras (all p-values >0.05). The latest US data suggests that HTK is at least non-inferior to UW for preserving DCD livers. These data support HTK use in DCD LT and contradict ILTS guidance.
